high_descs: Walk over to the section of counter to the left of the oven.
Open the cabinet door below the counter and take the white mug out of the cabinet, then close the door.
Turn right and walk towards the counter, then hang a right and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the mug inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and take out the now chilled mug then close the door.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the wooden shelving unit in the corner of the room.
Put the chilled white mug on the front edge of the middle shelf of the wooden shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled white mug on the middle shelf of a wooden shelving unit.

high_descs: Walk forward until you're even with the left side of the stove to your right and then turn right and walk to it once you're even with it.
Open the cupboard down to the left of the stove and get the mug that's under there before closing the door.
Turn right and walk until you're even with the fridge on your right and when you are turn right and walk to it.
Chill the mug in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the brown shelves.
Put the mug to the right of the orange cup.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold mug on the shelf.

high_descs: Go the small cabinet to the left of the stove
Take a mug out of the cabinet
Chill the mug in the fridge
Place the mug on a shelf
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug on a shelf
